                        data-ded="ded:ElementName">ded:ElementName: DedPurpose</xhtml:p>
                    <xhtml:p ism:ownerProducer="USA"
                        ism:classification="U"
                        data-ded="ded:ElementDefinition">ded:ElementDefinition: The prose that identifies and describes the reason and scope of the model (e.g., the output) about which this Data Element Dictionary is providing guidance.  If the source of the information contained in the DED is different from the DedHeader/edh/ResponsibleEntity, then the author should identify said source.</xhtml:p>
                    
                    <xhtml:p ism:ownerProducer="USA"
                        ism:classification="U"
                        data-ded="ded:ElementId">ded:ElementId: ded:DedPurpose</xhtml:p>
