                    <xhtml:p ism:ownerProducer="USA"
                        ism:classification="U"
                        data-ded="ded:ElementDefinition">ded:ElementDefinition: A short descriptor that characterizes the format and/or structure of the output about which this Data Element Dictionary is providing guidance.  The initial possible values are: Logical, UML, Physical, Ontology, Database, XML, JSON, CSV, CVE, and Other:SomeText.  Multiple values may be used. Additional details about the DED Model should be added to DedPurpose.</xhtml:p>
                    <xhtml:p ism:ownerProducer="USA"
                        ism:classification="U"
                        data-ded="ded:ElementId">ded:ElementId: ded:DedSubjectType</xhtml:p>
